Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}問題在這之後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.24,0:14:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}正如你所見 與Happy End相距甚遠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}結尾相當爛的結局
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這正是椎名落選最大的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}『我要離開油菜花莊』
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\bord0\shad0\fn華康竹風體W4\c&H6E6672&\frz346.4\move(780,694.668,598.667,440,23,4110)}永\N別\N了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我勸過很多遍了 讓她重新考慮一下結局
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是她完全不聽我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}『因為那是空太的願望』
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很好 很好哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}洋溢著疾馳感的青春
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.61,0:15:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我仿佛就像看到結局了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣的話 也許還有挽回的余地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}千尋老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了 神田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忘記東西了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果…不先從這裡開始的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那我先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這算什麼啊
