Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.54,0:22:36.83,NCED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}I'm dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.12,0:22:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an3\fs35}今後 這一點也不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.96,0:22:43.46,NCED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}迷いながら  涙を飲み込んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.96,0:22:43.46,NCED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}不斷迷茫著 逞強噙住眼角淚水
